The component already shows a bottom sheet on mobile, but it's custom-built:
- Has escape key handling
- Has swipe-to-close (sort of)
- Has backdrop
- Has drag handle

The new BottomSheet component will provide:
- Better swipe gesture handling via useDrag
- Consistent animation timing
- Proper focus management
- Accessibility improvements

